channel.title: Lifeless -> Remix Challenge <-
channel.description:
First of all, im sorry for my bad english and i hope everyone understand it XD
I posted a track named lifeless a month ago... So maybe someone want to remix it in a different style?

Lifeless: https://soundcloud.com/fruds-44960143/lifeless
If u want to remix write me in comments...
Deadline is 01.09.2019 (first of september)
